<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a id="headline-8"></a>龜老山展望公園的絕景</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在可以眺望瀨戶內海的島嶼和來島海峽大橋的</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">“</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">龜老山展望臺</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">”</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">結束你的旅程吧。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">這座展望臺位於愛媛縣今治市的大島，以建築師【隈研吾】的設計而聞名。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">被選為四國八十八景之一的珍貴景點，是遊覽島波海道的必遊景點。</span></p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
<div class="md:w-1/2 px-4"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2911" src="https://secure.j-bus.co.jp/busrepo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image7-11.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="428"></div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 px-4"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2912" src="https://secure.j-bus.co.jp/busrepo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image2-14.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="428"></div>
</div>
<table style="padding: 0px; width: 76.1252%; height: 264px;">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td style="width: 25.8534%; height: 24px;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt;">名稱</span></td>
<td style="width: 72.8308%; height: 24px;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">龜老山展望公園</span><br />
</span></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
